\{f_\alpha : \alpha > 0\}
 \Gamma(\alpha) = \int_0^\infty x^{\alpha-1} e^{-x}\,dx. 
 f_\alpha(x)=\begin{cases} \frac{x^{\alpha-1} e^{-x}}{\Gamma(\alpha)} & \text{for }x>0 \\[12pt] 0 & \text{for }x<0 \end{cases} 
 f_\alpha * f_\beta = f_{\alpha+\beta}\tag{1} 
